  "text": "As with any reference counting collector, this age-oriented algorithm cannot reclaim cyclic data structures in the old generation (cyclic structures in the young generation are collected immediately). To reclaim such structures, the tracing sliding view algorithm of [CITATION_1] is run infrequently on the full heap.",
